---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
const referralCode = "STAR-FSRJ-5N7Z";
---

<Layout
  title="Star Citizen Referral Code – How to Get the 50,000 UEC Bonus"
  description="Use a Star Citizen referral code during account creation and receive the official 50,000 UEC enlistment bonus. Step-by-step guide, 24-hour rule, reward ladder and FAQ explained."
>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="ref-hero">
  <img src="/assets/img/referral/star-citizen-referral-code-50000-uec-bonus-hero.webp"
       alt="Star Citizen referral code enlistment bonus 50,000 UEC"
       class="ref-hero-bg" />

  <div class="container ref-hero-content">
    <h1>Star Citizen Referral Code – How to Get the 50,000 UEC Bonus</h1>

    <p class="ref-hero-sub">
      Enter a referral code during account creation and start with bonus UEC.
      This guide explains exactly how it works and when to use it.
    </p>

    <div class="ref-hero-actions">
      <a href="https://robertsspaceindustries.com/enlist?referral=STAR-FSRJ-5N7Z" class="btn-primary">
        Create Account (Code Prefilled)
      </a>
      <a href="#how-to-use" class="btn-secondary">Step-by-step guide</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CODE STRIP -->
<section class="ref-code-bar">
  <div class="container ref-code-bar-inner">
    <div>
      <strong>Referral code: {referralCode}</strong> — Receive the official 50,000 UEC enlistment bonus.
      <span class="ref-code-note">Enter during signup or within 24 hours.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW TO USE + WHAT IS -->
<section id="how-to-use" class="container ref-grid-2">

  <div class="ref-card">
    <h2>How to use a Star Citizen referral code</h2>

    <ol class="ref-steps">
      <li>Create your RSI account.</li>
      <li>Enter <strong>{referralCode}</strong> in the referral field.</li>
      <li>Complete registration.</li>
      <li>Activate your account with a starter package.</li>
    </ol>

    <p class="ref-callout">
      Best practice: use the prefilled signup link to avoid typing errors.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="ref-card">
    <h2>What is a Star Citizen referral code?</h2>

    <p>
      A referral code is part of Star Citizen’s official Recruit Program.
      New players can enter a code during account creation to receive a starting bonus in UEC (United Earth Credits).
    </p>

    <p>
      It does not change the game price, does not lock you into anything,
      and does not provide unfair advantages — it simply gives you additional starting funds.
    </p>

    <p>
      Once your account becomes active, you receive your own referral code
      and can participate in the recruit reward ladder.
    </p>
  </div>

</section>

<!-- WHAT DO YOU GET -->
<section class="container ref-card">

  <h2>What do you get with 50,000 UEC?</h2>

  <p>
    50,000 UEC won’t buy you a new ship — but it meaningfully improves your first hours.
    It reduces early friction and allows you to focus on learning the game instead of recovering from small mistakes.
  </p>

  <table class="ref-table">
    <tr>
      <th>Category</th>
      <th>How it helps early on</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Armor & FPS Gear</td>
      <td>Equip a full basic loadout and replace gear after early mistakes.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Ship Operations</td>
      <td>Cover refuel, rearm and minor repair costs without interrupting gameplay.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Starter Upgrades</td>
      <td>Experiment with small component improvements and optimize your ship.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Utility Tools</td>
      <td>Purchase multitool attachments and early mission essentials.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Margin for Errors</td>
      <td>Absorb early losses without forcing unnecessary grind.</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p>
    In practical terms, the referral bonus gives you breathing room during onboarding.
    It makes your first sessions smoother and more flexible.
  </p>

</section>

<!-- 24 HOUR RULE -->
<section class="container ref-card">
  <h2>The 24-hour rule explained</h2>

  <p>
    If you forget to enter a referral code during account creation,
    you can still add one within 24 hours after registering your RSI account.
  </p>

  <p>
    After this window closes, the code can no longer be applied.
    That’s why it is strongly recommended to enter the code immediately during signup.
  </p>
</section>

<!-- REWARD LADDER -->
<section class="container ref-card">
  <h2>How the recruit reward ladder works</h2>

  <p>
    Once your account is active, you receive your own referral code.
    Every successful recruit grants you referral points.
  </p>

  <p>
    Over time, these points unlock reward tiers ranging from cosmetic items
    to higher-tier collectibles.
  </p>

  <p>
    The referral ladder is designed as a long-term community progression system —
    the immediate value for new players remains the 50,000 UEC starting bonus.
  </p>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="container ref-card">
  <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

  <details>
    <summary>Can I add a referral code later?</summary>
    <p>Yes, within 24 hours after creating your account.</p>
  </details>

  <details>
    <summary>When do I receive the 50,000 UEC?</summary>
    <p>After account activation with a starter package.</p>
  </details>

  <details>
    <summary>Does using a referral code cost anything?</summary>
    <p>No, it is completely free.</p>
  </details>

  <details>
    <summary>Can I change the referral code later?</summary>
    <p>No. Once applied and after 24 hours, it cannot be modified.</p>
  </details>

  <details>
    <summary>Is this an official system?</summary>
    <p>Yes. The referral program is operated directly by RSI.</p>
  </details>

</section>

<section class="container ref-final-cta">
  <h2>Start smart from day one</h2>
  <a href="https://robertsspaceindustries.com/enlist?referral=STAR-FSRJ-5N7Z" class="btn-gold">
    Create Account & Get 50,000 UEC
  </a>
</section>

</Layout>
